      <title>美国经济基础稳固，有望支持美联储维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/us-economy-on-solid-footing-set-to-back-fed-s-interest-rate-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在健康的消费者支出的推动下，美国经济在 2024 年最后阶段仍保持着舒适的巡航速度，并与全球同行拉开了更大的差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/us-economy-on-solid-footing-set-to-back-fed-s-interest-rate-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>风险成为动荡债务市场的避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/risk-becomes-a-safe-haven-in-volatile-debt-market-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在如今混乱的信贷世界中，风险债券在波动时期的表现优于安全债券。原因何在？人们越来越关注利息收入，或者用行业术语来说就是利差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/risk-becomes-a-safe-haven-in-volatile-debt-market-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meloni 称 Mediobanca 的竞标反映了 Monte Paschi 的实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/mediobanca-bid-reflects-monte-paschi-s-strength-meloni-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼称，锡耶纳银行（Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA）对竞争对手 Mediobanca SpA 的收购是一次“市场操作”，反映了这家复苏后的银行的实力。]]></description>
